{"tid":1957846,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想入沙嶺拜手足既入一入黎 教你去","createTime":"2020-04-04T07:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T06:52:24.000Z","uid":36091,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc76748326b087d56478e2f7273d8afdd7199d9","tid":1957846,"uid":36091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"我分享我自己既方法 有其他方式去既 就分享下啦<br />\n首先用你既方法去上水巴士總站 坐九巴 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">73K</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n去到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「沙嶺」</strong></span>落車<br />\n落車會見到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGdpcnp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGdpcnp.png&h=fa90c3f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"878c6a3fb6bf8752ea3e42ace62850bfc891971f","tid":1957846,"uid":36091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:54:38.000Z","msg":"之後望下巴士站地下 早前已經有手足留左指引<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YvJsUE7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYvJsUE7.png&h=42cb1101&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dad3130efd25191669545674f98108ffed403de","tid":1957846,"uid":35600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716cce867b15382be1d951d482e79a3a42b86f0d","tid":1957846,"uid":36091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:00:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HwB9725.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwB9725.png&h=55fe5f27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"791f68c408eeb38e2ec7538c2a44c8f5b447d97f","tid":1957846,"uid":320211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"👍🏻"},{"pid":"35687e36c8061377ae6b0ab07c4ef3043b2a4081","tid":1957846,"uid":36091,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-0